data.description: Charming 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath townhome in the heart of Village of Sandalwood Lakes in West Palm Beach.  All tile floors downstairs with upgraded kitchen and a private courtyard patio creates an oasis as a secondary outdoor living space. The primary suite features a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom. This property is move in ready while also hosting so many opportunities to shape your own home aesthetic. Super close proximity to downtown West Palm Beach, Palm Beach Island and the beaches. Retail and restaurants are both at your fingertips from this location.  Community has 3 amazing park areas with pools, tennis, walk parks, soccer fields. Maintenance fee includes so much! Cable, water and trash, roof maintenance and exterior building insurance - only insure the interior!
